flowchart TD
    %% Harness Maintenance Loop — All 5 modes

    START([Invoke /harness-maintain]) --> MODE{Select Mode}:::decision

    %% Mode Paths
    MODE -->|Create Mode| CREATE["Create Mode<br/>(Harness missing)"]:::improve
    CREATE --> CREATE_WORK["Run starter-init bootstrap<br/>Build initial constitution & security baseline"]:::improve

    MODE -->|Assess Mode| ASSESS["Assess Mode<br/>(Audit health score)"]:::assess
    ASSESS --> ASSESS_WORK["Score (1-5) against 6 subsystems<br/>Generate harness-assessment.md"]:::assess

    MODE -->|Improve Mode| IMPROVE["Improve Mode<br/>(Observability triage)"]:::improve
    IMPROVE --> IMPROVE_WORK["Read memories/repo/harness-telemetry.md<br/>Apply durable fixes to constitution / config"]:::improve

    MODE -->|Eval Mode| EVAL["Eval Mode<br/>(Split evaluation)"]:::assess
    EVAL --> EVAL_WORK["Run split evaluator passes<br/>Generate feature execution eval-report.md"]:::assess

    %% End Connection
    CREATE_WORK --> ENDS([Harness baseline verified & healthy]):::terminal
    ASSESS_WORK --> ENDS
    IMPROVE_WORK --> ENDS
    EVAL_WORK --> ENDS

    classDef terminal fill:#0d0d0d,stroke:#0d0d0d,color:#fff
    classDef decision fill:#fff7ed,stroke:#f59e0b,color:#0d0d0d
    classDef assess fill:#eef2ff,stroke:#c7d2fe,color:#3730a3
    classDef improve fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#ffc107,color:#b45309

    class START,ENDS terminal
